dominants.dominant_desc:
Maintain the line of troops and dont be overwhelmed;
Try to get as much experience and gold coins as possible;
 Dont chase randomly, wait for the equipment to take shape before looking for opportunities;
 If the opponent is suppressing you from a distance, first fill the line first.
 In the mid term, pay attention to level upgrading and wait for the equipment to take shape.
 Use skill cycles to create combos: After each skill is released, the basic attack will be connected to the passive attack speed.
 Online Rhythm: If you can suppress the lane alone, after clearing the lane, immediately move to the jungle to support the middle lane to help teammates establish jungle advantages and seize neutral resources.
